Fourth Department,

January, 1947.

(January 8, 1947.) John J. O’Haire et al., Respondents, v. Wanda Stegelske, Appellant.

Judgment affirmed, with costs. All concur. (The judgment is for plaintiffs in an action to compel specific performance.) Present — Taylor, P. J., Dowling, Harris, McCurn and Larkin, JJ.
